works.description: Renowned luxury luggage company Tumi has lately announced its partnership with Italian motorcycle maker Ducati for a new collection that launches this Autumn. The collection features performance-driven travel and lifestyle accessories, including three sporty red travel cases, one backpack, a crossbody bag and two vibrant red duffels - a larger Due Porte Collapsible Wheeled Duffel and an easy-to-carry Actuator Sport Duffel.
